dc_title_s: Latest pictorial road map of Delhi and  New Delhi with railways and general information.
dc_description_s: Nirdosh Publications. [Cover title: Delhi guide with latest pictorial road map of Delhi & New Delhi. Places of interest represented pictorially.] Ancillary maps: "Diplomatic Colony (Chanakya Puri)," "Connaught Place," and Viney Nagar area. Map shows land management areas by government agency. Accompanied by: Delhi guide with pictorial road map of Delhi, 37 p.; Map library does not have this guide.
